B Derivation of the Approximation to Knowledge Control Guidance
We derive the approximation to the knowledge control guided denoising transition (5) following [4]. We rewrite (5) to (8) using a normalization constant Z that normalizes Z e‚àíŒªF ‚à•Uœï(zt,t,y)‚àíF0(y)‚à•dzt = 1:

pŒ∏,œï(zt|zt+1, y, F0) = pŒ∏(zt|zt+1, zcond) ¬∑ Ze‚àíŒªF ‚à•Uœï(zt,t,y)‚àíF0(y)‚à•.

